    mistake: 'Applying powerful behavioral-reinforcement techniques (variable rewards, notification-driven reinforcement loops) without considering whether the resulting habit genuinely serves the user\'s own interest, or only the product\'s engagement metrics — see Positive Design Ethics for the relevant test.',
