    mistake: 'Using an auto-dismissing toast for genuinely critical information requiring guaranteed acknowledgment — the pattern\'s automatic disappearance means important messages can be entirely missed.',
    interview: 'Distinguishing which information genuinely warrants a toast versus a more persistent notification pattern demonstrates appropriate stakes-matching.',
