    mistake: 'Letting a copilot silently modify a user\'s existing work without a clear, explicit approval step — this breaks trust and a sense of ownership over the work.',
    interview: 'Explaining how you\'d visually distinguish AI suggestions from a user\'s own content shows practical copilot-UX pattern knowledge.',
