    title: 'Citation & Source Attribution',
    def: 'Linking AI-generated claims back to the specific source documents or data they were derived from, enabling users to verify accuracy and trace information to its origin.',
    why: 'Citation is one of the most effective, concrete tools for combating misplaced trust in AI output, converting an unverifiable claim into a checkable one and giving users agency over their own trust calibration.',
