    examples: [
      { label: 'Example · Constraint-aware edge AI design', text: 'An industrial monitoring system used a lightweight model optimized specifically for its edge device\'s limited compute and power budget, and handled intermittent connectivity to central systems gracefully.' },
      { label: 'Example · Constraint-blind edge AI design', text: 'A team deployed a compute-heavy model unsuited to their edge hardware\'s actual power and processing constraints, causing frequent performance issues and battery drain.' },
    ],
    mistake: 'Deploying a compute-heavy model to edge hardware without accounting for its actual power and processing constraints — edge deployment needs models specifically optimized for that hardware\'s limits.',
